androidx.car.app

Class CarListDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • Dialog
      • androidx.car.app.CarListDialog

  • public class CarListDialog
extends Dialog
    A subclass of Dialog that is tailored for the car environment. This dialog can display a fixed list of items. There is no affordance for setting titles or any other text.

    Its functionality is similar to if a list has been set on AlertDialog, but is styled so that it is more appropriate for displaying in vehicles.

    Note that this dialog cannot be created with an empty list.
